{"tid":2414352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生推警今被裁定襲警罪成 判囚5星期","createTime":"2021-02-19T10:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T13:56:23.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"489cf8b498d93632737aeb085ead07a248bb0e58","tid":2414352,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"前年8.31太子站事件兩個月，網民在旺角一帶發起悼念活動，及後演變成警民衝突。有男學生被指用雙手推警員，早前就襲警罪受審。裁判官施祖堯今裁決時指，被告自辯不合情理，若被告是無辜被撞失平衡下用雙手推了前方警員一下，<span class=\"red\">被告當時理應澄清而非逃跑，故認為唯一合理解釋是被告自知作出違法的觸碰</span>，因此裁定被告罪成，判監5星期。<br />\n<br />\n辯方曾質疑警方證人在書面供詞中指，被告當時推了龍背部左邊近中間一下，跟他在庭上表示被告推了龍背部的左後方有矛盾。施官認為是吹毛求疵。<br />\n<br />\n由於<span class=\"red\">被告在裁決後承認控罪內行為</span>，施官考慮到若判入更生中心或勞教中心等處所，拘留時間對於本案而言實屬太長，基於被告有悔意和初犯等，終判以5星期監禁。被告的家人在旁聽席上聞判落淚。"},{"pid":"2fb164a4514c7736c893b1d559839d6c894e7c53","tid":2414352,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/F7OI6XKSQRB3FJPHL6BUIUA2DI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2FF7OI6XKSQRB3FJPHL6BUIUA2DI%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=8e4c49d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2FF7OI6XKSQRB3FJPHL6BUIUA2DI%2F&h=59912a64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/F7OI6XKSQRB3FJPHL6BUIUA2DI/</a>"},{"pid":"baacbeeaeb123d2dbd8f03cb0370f7b1cfa4e2fe","tid":2414352,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"咁都五星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且會留案底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d40f3adb854be96c0e81c4b608e1322c3c8a28",